[SN]TITLE[SN]
Skye woolskin business secures funding from HIE

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Scotland's only commercial-scale woolskin tannery has secured funding towards improvements to its business.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Skyeskyns Ltd based in Waternish in north west Skye is one of just two businesses of its kind in the UK.
Highlands and Islands Enterprise (HIE) has announced investment of Â£33,360 in the family-run firm's construction of a new building.
HIE said the development would help to secure the future of 18 jobs and increase turnover by about a third.
